    {
      "id": "HTRhDL2L1e-dCkl6qACaK",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6597.444444444444,
      "y": 3419,
      "width": 660,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1308448750,
      "version": 427,
      "versionNonce": 120857330,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1767001758789,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "我想设计这样一个子游戏，方块只能在地图上移动\n每次移动一次是滚动的方式移动到终点就算胜利\n方块的垂直方向可以叠加比如两个方块那么每次移动翻滚就会占两个格子\n\n\n问题：地图该怎么自动化生成？地图的生成逻辑怎么和我的方块数量匹配？\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 168,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "我想设计这样一个子游戏，方块只能在地图上移动\n每次移动一次是滚动的方式移动到终点就算胜利\n方块的垂直方向可以叠加比如两个方块那么每次移动翻滚就会占两个格子\n\n\n问题：地图该怎么自动化生成？地图的生成逻辑怎么和我的方块数量匹配？\n",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "FSfI7itAFs8lgt8x15kPw",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6575.444444444444,
      "y": 3714,
      "width": 952.5599365234375,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
